---
---

<section class="bench-cta">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="cta-inner">
      <p class="eyebrow">
        <span>Run it yourself</span>
      </p>

      <h2 class="display">
        Don't trust the numbers?<br/>
        <em class="accent">Reproduce them.</em>
      </h2>

      <p class="lede">
        The corpus is public. The CLI is open source. Clone the repo, run <code>koji bench</code> against any category, and compare your numbers to ours. No sign-up, no vendor lock-in, no "contact sales to see the benchmark."
      </p>

      <div class="cta-code">
        <pre><span class="tok-prompt">$</span> git clone https://github.com/getkoji/corpus
<span class="tok-prompt">$</span> pip install koji-cli
<span class="tok-prompt">$</span> koji bench --corpus ./corpus --category insurance</pre>
      </div>

      <div class="cta-actions">
        <a href="https://github.com/getkoji/corpus" class="btn btn-primary">
          Browse the corpus
          <span class="arrow">→</span>
        </a>
        <a href="https://docs.getkoji.dev/getting-started/" class="btn btn-ghost">
          Install Koji
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .bench-cta {
    padding: var(--section-pad) 0;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
  }

  .cta-inner {
    max-width: 820px;
  }

  h2.display {
    font-size: clamp(2.25rem, 5.5vw, 4rem);
    line-height: 1.02;
    letter-spacing: -0.03em;
    margin: 0.75rem 0 1.25rem;
    text-wrap: balance;
  }

  .display .accent {
    color: var(--vermillion);
    font-style: italic;
    font-variation-settings: 'opsz' 144, 'SOFT' 100;
  }

  .lede {
    max-width: 62ch;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .lede code {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.88em;
    background: var(--cream-2);
    padding: 0.1em 0.4em;
    border-radius: 2px;
    color: var(--ink);
  }

  .cta-code {
    background: var(--ink);
    color: var(--cream-2);
    padding: 1.5rem 1.75rem;
    border-radius: 3px;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-md);
    overflow-x: auto;
  }

  .cta-code pre {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.88rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
    color: var(--cream-2);
    margin: 0;
  }

  .tok-prompt {
    color: var(--vermillion);
    user-select: none;
  }

  .cta-actions {
    display: flex;
    gap: 0.85rem;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  @media (max-width: 560px) {
    .cta-actions {
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: stretch;
    }
    .btn {
      justify-content: center;
    }
  }
</style>
